{"author":"Claude","data":{"alias":"chubby-night-owl","assignee":"claude","description":"## Why\n\nMCP tools carry no behavior annotations, so clients cannot present safe UI or\nconfirmation flows. rebar already has the semantic information internally —\nreads are separate from writes, writes are hidden under `REBAR_MCP_READONLY`,\nJira-live and LLM tools are call-gated — but none of it is exposed as the MCP\n`ToolAnnotations` hints (`readOnlyHint`, `destructiveHint`, `idempotentHint`,\n`openWorldHint`) that the spec defines for exactly this purpose.\n\n## What\n\nAnnotate every registered tool via `FastMCP.tool(annotations=ToolAnnotations(...))`\nacross the three registrars (`register_read_tools` in `_mcp_reads.py`,\n`register_llm_tools` in `_mcp_llm.py`, `register_write_tools` in `_mcp_writes.py`).\nConfirmed feasible: `mcp` 1.28.1 exposes `ToolAnnotations` with all four hint\nfields and `FastMCP.tool` accepts `annotations`.\n\nMapping policy:\n\n- **Read tools** -> `readOnlyHint: true`.\n- **Additive writes** (create/comment/tag/link/edit/claim/transition/set_*) ->\n  `readOnlyHint: false`, `destructiveHint: false`; `idempotentHint: true` where\n  the op is idempotent (e.g. tag/untag).\n- **Destructive/irreversible** (archive/delete/compact, reconcile-live) ->\n  `destructiveHint: true`.\n- **Outward-reaching** (LLM review/verify, Jira reconcile, `run_workflow`) ->\n  `openWorldHint: true`.\n\n## Scope\n\n`src/rebar/_mcp_reads.py`, `_mcp_llm.py`, `_mcp_writes.py`. Annotations are hints\nonly — no behavior change. Add/adjust a parity test if the interface suite pins\ntool metadata.\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n- [ ] Every `@mcp.tool()` in the three registrars carries a `ToolAnnotations`\n  consistent with the mapping policy above.\n- [ ] Read tools are `readOnlyHint: true`; delete/archive/reconcile-live are\n  `destructiveHint: true`; LLM/Jira/workflow tools are `openWorldHint: true`.\n- [ ] The server still builds and starts; existing MCP/interface tests pass.\n- [ ] No functional behavior of any tool changes.","id":"fce6-d90a-9a9d-4254","parent_id":"b02d-10bc-07ee-49e7","priority":2,"tags":[],"ticket_type":"story","title":"Annotate MCP tools with behavior hints (read-only/destructive/idempotent/open-world)"},"env_id":"58e9f32e-f999-436d-9c1a-5d0eef5c9903","event_type":"CREATE","timestamp":1783148925412742097,"uuid":"b7c78cce-6f21-451f-8530-2a59f5dc8858"}